sources.title: Enter the Devil (1972) Western, Horror | Joshua Bryant, Irene Kelly, David Cass | Full Movie
sources.description:
It's Too Late For Exorcism!
Somewhere in south west Texas, where a christian cult is said to have resided in the past, a deputy sheriff investigates a number of suspicious deaths.

This movie is subtitled !

Director: Frank Q. Dobbs
Writers: Frank Q. Dobbs, David S. Cass Sr.
Stars: Joshua Bryant, Irene Kelly, David S. Cass Sr.
Genres: Horror, Thriller, Western

metadata.Plot: People are disappearing in the outskirts of a Texan town, which leads to loss of business from a lodge. The sheriff dismisses the incident as mere accidents, only worrying about his re-election campaign, but an occult researcher investigates and alleges that a devil worshiping cult might be responsible.
